        "id": 1001907
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-09-27T20:19:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "discussed offline:\n  * git is the primary (by orders of magnitude) use-case.\n  * yes, but the computation for \u0027DIFF v MODIFIED\u0027 could become more complex with e.g. commit position and/or fetch_ref consideration.",
      "parentUuid": "692b0edf_ee232b36",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 118,
        "startChar": 10,
        "endLine": 118,
        "endChar": 27
      },
      "revId": "1380f894a3d9f317ed84054ea4ac9c52bd49893b",
